transcript.text: Welcome to On Print Shop.
Today we will see design tool enhancement in On Print Shop version 6.2 and how it benefits for our printers.
So these are the key features for Design Tools.
First is the promotional product and for this we have additional option mapping with design tool size and attribute via stock management, zoom and usability enhancement.
After that we have phone based studio enhancements.
For that we have PDF block, text area editor, image quality check, auto update preview and multiple page PDF file.
After that we have improved user experience.
For that we have template wise, multiple back filter, masking, border studio help message and alerts.
First we will see promotional product enhancement and for that we have additional option mapping with design tool.
So how it will be useful to us for that if we'll go in our admin panel.
So this is our promotional product of T-shirt man half sleeves.
So if you will go in promotional tab there we have added one feature over there of bandwidth additional option and there is the three option of yes, no and allow edit on additional option page.
So if you select yes option then you can map your additional option with promotional product colour or additional background images.
And after that you can select the additional options.
So once I'll go in storefront in our design studio.
So this is our promotional product and after that user can easily select the colours from here.
After that we will see size and attribute wise stock management.
So you can manage your stock in promotional product with the size and attribute wise.
So here is the option of stock in admin panel.
So once I'll select the attribute options over here, then I just need to save it.
So once I'll save it from here, I can manage my stock the attributewise.
So you can manage your stock with size and attributewise after that we'll see form based studio enhancement.
And 1st we have PDF block text area editor.
So what will happen over here then in PDF block where you just want to format your text area so you can easily format your virtual blocks more efficient way.
And after that once the system will automatically add related text for your blog and it will reduce the possibility of error while writing your text.
So you just need to select the formatting and system will automatically generate the syntax over there.
After that we will see the improved user experience.
And 1st we have the mask.
So we have added one new feature for mask where the user will be able to apply different mask on the images in the designer studio.
So if I'll go in designer studio so here is the image which I have selected.
After that, once I'll go and mask images over there.
Now we just want to apply mask over this in images.
Then we just need to select the image over here.
Then we'll go edit option over here.
Then we have the option of mask and border.
So once I'll click over there in mask.
So these are the different mask options available over here.
You can select an appropriate mask.
Then you are able to apply mask images.
So this all other mask images available over here.
So that is how you are able to manage your masks.
After that this is the borders.
So user will be able to select the colour of the border and width of the border which to be applied on the image.
So here is the option of border.
So from here you can select the colour of the border whichever you just want to select.
After that you can select the size of that which is the 7.
So this is your border.
So that is how you can apply border on that image.
After that we have enhanced 7 filters to add effects in your personalized or selected images.
For that you just need to go over here and added option.
After that, this is the option of filters over here.
So once I click on filters.
So from here you can apply filters on your images.
These are the seven different effects available over here like brownie, vintage black, white, Technicolor, sepia and polarite.
So these all are the effects available over here.
You can select any of the effect which you want.
So these are the studio features of on Friendshop version 6.2.
Thank you.
